  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that's how we arrived to Czernowitz, which used to be the capital of Bukovina.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from then, we were only two hours away by train, approximately two hours away by train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But again, there were no trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Czernowitz had just been occupied when we arrived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had had some relatives there who lived there before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We tried to find them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't believe we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But what happened a few days after we were there was that the Russians started capturing men on the street, regardless of who they were, and dragged them deep into Russia to have them work in the cold mine-- in the coal mines to help the war effort.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were snatching anybody who was on the street, shoving them into trucks, not even letting them tell their families what happened to them, and-- and take them away.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, when we heard that, we decide-- the men were the decision makers, of course, at that time-- they decided to rent a truck.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we escaped to Kishinev, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which had been occupied from earlier times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So this capturing of man or people on the street had already finished by that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we lived in a room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was this woman who rented us this room, but the room didn't have a door to the outside.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she would not allow us to go through her room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the only way to get into our room was through the window.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were going in and out through the window.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we were there for a few months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember anything about what I did there during the day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we started walking again.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
